Its DinoTRON, logomorph. Not DinoBOT. 
Stegotron and Dinotron were running down the hall, when all of a sudden the  hall autoguns began fireing on them. They ducked and crawled past the autoguns. Dinotron fired his optic blasters a couple of times and dismantled one of them. They finally reached Triceradon and Ultracon who were pounding on the door.
Stegotron: "Uh guys, Why don't you push the button to open the door? "
"Oh." they said. They pushed the button and the door slid open. They burst in with all their guns a blazing.
